text:
"Do dost, Ek chaabi", "Do bottle, Ek hi m paani", "Do balti, Ek magga", "Do saal, Ek roomie" aur "Do raah, Ek saphar"....
Tujhe roomie banane ka life decision m abhi tk nhi top kr paya hu. Shukla ko kabhi dikkat hi nhi hoti h. Chahe light jali ho, speaker baj rhe ho, movie chal rhi ho, bhai khali paani dhundta tha aur wo bhi naa mile to so jaata tha. 
Chai ka ever ready partner aur mera veg saathi. Bhagwaan m utna hi believe krta h jitna iron man m (i literally saw him cry after his death in a movie... RIP). Aur ab to weebs bhi bann chuke h hum dono (Thanks for my first anime bro.... Kimi no Na wa <3)
Bhut miss krunga yr tere harr 5 min wale alarms ko aur tere saath kre gye harr tareeke k discussions ko. Exam se pehle bhagwaan k bhajan kaun sunega ab saath aur kaun dega mujhe machchar daani.
Thanks for being always by my side bro, Harr HC ki trip k liye, room ka nahane ka equilibrium banaye rkhne k liye, harr mech k saphar k liye.
All the best bro for the future now. Itna determined hona asaan nhi hota jitna tu h. Hope we meet again soon and you have a better motivating speech ready this time lol.
Baah for life. Goodbye. Take Care.
author: Kratik  Jain

text:
Arraaaaaay isko nhi dena tha ğŸ˜‚

Bhai tere m itna energy kaise aata h. Chal Fifa khelte h, chal canteen chalte h, chal order karte h ğŸ˜‚ yahi sab bolte hue paya jaata h tu. 1st year m bhut halla machaya h tumne wing m. Green bomb saale tu hi laya mini militia m sabse pehle. Teri wajah se pareshaan hogye log. Suicidal tendency game se hi thi tujhe to ğŸ˜‚ Phir bhi kuch bhi bolo dil ka bhut acha insaan h yr tu. Kisi ko bura na lag jaye iska pura dhyaan rkhta h tu yaa help karne k liye hamesha ready rahna. Tere muh se to gaali bhi meethi lagti h yr itna pyaara h tu. Aur waise mera naam mini militia m Ludos tha Lodus nhi to wo kyun bulata h ğŸ˜‚. 

Ek aur trip maarte h yr khali uttarakhand se kya hoga. jaisi sexy photos tune daal rakhi h idhar waise aur bhi to chahiye naa. Miss your pizza experiments bro. bhut bure pizza se ache pizza tk sab khaya h tere kahne pe ğŸ˜‚. Fifa m tune mujhe thodi bhut baar hara to diya but saale aur tactics to laga cross krne k alawa. Sports chalu krde yr khelna kab tk chess khelega ğŸ˜‚. Chal jyada troll nhi karunga nhi to agli baar veg bolke anda mangwa lega tu XD. Tujhme alag hi spring h bhai, jaha dekho waha koodane lgega, chadne lgega matlab bhai aaram se ğŸ˜‚. Lekin tere chm102 aur DS ka rr bhut yaad aayega. Everything is cool and fun until Goel gets serious. Khaskar intern k time pe (i understand tho ;)) Tere cooler ne bhut tshirt phaadi h saale (meri bhi) Lekin maza bhi aata tha tere cooler m garmi m. World cup aur kitni baar aake so jaata tha m tumhare room pe.

Bas aise hi energy inject karta rha, Pizza khilata rha (acha wala please) aur practice kr bhut fifa m nhi to kabhi nhi hara payega mukesh aur mujhe ğŸ˜‚. Paiso ki chinta bhi chodd de ab bahut kamane wala h, jitna bachaya h saara kharch kar daal humpe aur aane wali kisi pe :p Aur dosto ko bhi message kar liya kar yaar kabhi :p

Chal aur batana milne pe. Take care. Mera bhai â¤ï¸
author: Kratik  Jain

text:
Pandey bolna thoda ajeeb lgta h yr tujhe sb wahi bolte h. You deserve a nickname bhai ab to... rakh denge wo bhi ğŸ˜‚

1st year m kya jungle tha bhai tumhara room. Best kutte ka impression aaj tk tujhse hi dekha h. Sam ko itna molest kre ho ki ab Sam kya seedhe phansi milegi. lekin inn first year walon ko tumne hi khola h ğŸ˜‚ Itna energy/tharak kaise tha tum m pehle saal se hi ğŸ˜‚ Bilkul clear goal tha tumhara shuru se hi branch change maaro coding kro aur paisa kamao, bilkul sophisticated banane ka try nhi kra tumne (which i really appreciate man) bhut enthu tha tum m padne ka aur notes banane ka 2-3 saal tk. acha h dheere dheere seekh gye reality lol. kitni bhi tareef krdu lekin ek cheez ki kbhi nhi kr paunga aur wo h tumhari writing ğŸ˜‚ notes banane ka fayda kya agar hamare kaam nhi aaye to saale

Itne course kre h saath m (ds included jisko krne k liye tumne G ka zor lga diya lol) aur sb m aakhri min tk assignment krna aur phir sam ki haalat dekhke khush hona ğŸ˜‚. phatta acha chalu kra tha yr apn ne maza aata h tha badiya. tumhara lamba ki fast ball pe chidna ğŸ˜‚. Spo m rhke kitne logo ki baatein suni hongi kaise kr lete ho ye sb. sbka rr, sbki gaaliyan, sbke dukh ğŸ˜‚. mene placement k time jb rant kra tha tumhare messenger pe and then deleted them and you called me after that man, That was special bro â¤ï¸. Harr baar good news tumne hi di h mujhe to intern ki bhi placement ki bhi. 
intern k interview k time bada dilasa bhi diya tumne aur anime fans se hello seekhna (lol what were we thinking). but pata tha sbko pandey h to chill h (itni respect pandey kaise handle kriğŸ˜‚). tumhari intern lgne par bhi sbse pehle gale apn hi lage the hostel m ğŸ˜

pyaare aadmi ho tum yr. koi fake coolness nhi, koi boasting nhi. tumhari aankhe bhai kitni bhaari h seriously. kuch bhi thoda sad bolte ho jb to dard dikhta h yr unme ğŸ¥º. tumhare paseene wale hugs aur man (.)(.) to bhut hi unique h mere liye ğŸ˜‚ aise hi pyaar phalate rho jisse milo. bhut stories sunnani h abhi tumhe humko to yaad rkhna unko. Man in Black to apn h hi ğŸ˜ To aise hi haste rho, stories sunate rho, mahol banate rho, kaam aate rho ğŸ˜‚( P.S. mujhe pata h ki tumne mera summer m eco nhi bhara tha ğŸ˜). Tumhare saath trip bachi hui h to wo to krke hi rhenge aur wo bhi tumhare dream pay ke 1.5 times bache hue paiso se ğŸ˜‚
P.S: Love you â¤ï¸
P.P.S: Sam se hi puchle ğŸ˜

text:
The most respectable person for me in the college. How you influence others around you is so graceful. Naa jaane kitne course me assist kra h mujhe tune. 1st year to pura saath hi nikla h, roll no. bhi aaspass aur wing m bhi harr samay saath. Hope my P.E. instructions paid off XD. One of my few Veg saathi bhi h tu (par anda bhi khata h lol). Shubham Tharwani ki bitching nahi rukni chahiye in general bhi.
Remember shayad 1st year me ek baar apn roof pe gye the btop ki and there we discussed our stories and crushes and what not lol. Hope we meet up soon and make up for the missing stories. Till then Chaapta rha aur bhul na jaana yr. 
P.S. Watch seedhi pehanane laga kya finally XD

text:
Hey Baby (Read it in your voice ğŸ˜‚)
Literally the most caring person in the campus. Naa Jaane humne aisa kya kra ki tum itni care karne lage hamari. Tere bina sahi m Degree puri nhi ho paati meri to. Hamesha last moment pe cycle maangne aata tha tumse lab k liye aur agar tumhari kisi aur k pass hoti thi to jugaad bhi karwa dete the tum. Ek baar to mene tumhari chaabi bhi kho diti aur tumhari cycle gate k cycle stand pe raha gyi thi aur tab bhi tumhi mujhe cycle pe baithake gate tk le gye the <3. Your constant hugs are what i will miss the most. Kabhi lonely feel hi nhi hone diya tumne. Hamesha canteen chalne k liye ready aur fifa khelne ke liye bhi. I dont remember but shayad fifa ka addiction mere wajah se hi laga h tumhe ğŸ˜‚. Last 1-2 saal to mene tumhe goel yaa najan k room pe fifa khelte hue hi dekha h bas. Yaa agar pizza kha rhe hote the to share hamesha karte the tum.
Hamesha respectful conversation aur discussion karne k liye (despite people using the state card XD) bhut respect badd gyi h tumhari hamare liye. Ek hi trip kra saath m Uttrakhand wala but wo bhi itna legendary aur memorable. Thank you for trusting my driving skills the most ;) Pure trip m mere saath hi rahe tum. Bas thoda darna kam karo yr :p Ab to life m bhut cliffs se kudna hoga. Tumhare dost hamesha saath h tumhare <3 Ab to old rajendra nagar bhi nikal loge tum. Agar mein delhi aaya to Sam k liye bhi jang hogi ğŸ˜‚ Jo bhi ho apan to touch m rahne hi h bs tum aise hi khush, caring aur strong bane raho. 
Love you bro <3
P.S. Fifa m kab harayoge hume yr ğŸ˜‚ kitni practice aur. Lekin apna goal karne ke baad celebration mat bhulna. wahi favorite part h mera ğŸ˜‚.
author: Kratik  Jain

text:
Yo Rajababu !!
A perfect chick magnet :p Chaapu, Photographer, Sports, Raees ;), gym aur kitna bole thakk jayenge. Baaki andar se bhut motivating aur ache insaan ho yaar tum. Hagge ke iss side ko hagge ke uss side se connect krne wale link the tum XD. lucky charm ho tum mere liye ;) tumhare blazer se hi interview diya intern ka aur agar ab bangalore aana hua to sabse pass tum hi ho :)) Game Theory m bhi kya kaata yr mam ne apna lmao XD. Tumhari stories bhi kaafi badiya h ladkiyon k maamle m ;pp 
Uttrakhand ki trip bhai bhut sexy thi. khaas kr wo chadai pe scooty bhai (sorry uss time mukesh ko tumse churane ke liye :p) Tum me gazab ka leadership aura h yaar. Sabko saath rakhna aur motivate karte rahna is what i admire the most about you. Bhut curious bhi ho tum, Sab try karte ho (mini militia pro bhi bann gye the ek time pe to) Aur ab to IAS bhi bann jayoge to yaad rakhna XD
Bas aise hi saath banaye rakho aur bhi kayi jagah saath photo khichani h ;) All the best Tab Tak apne naye adventure k liye 
P.S. ek trip aur plan karte h yaar 
P.P.S. Camera ki photo bhi daaldo yaar drive pe :p

text:
Arre Shashi sir kya hi bolu aapke baare m. Bhut positive, bhut hasmukh, aur bhut calm insaan ho yr tum. Kayi baar tumhari wajah se hi din ki pehli smile hoti thi. Soke utho late, thoda mood off hota tha and then canteen m yaa wing m shashi dikh jaaye to bs smile aa jaati thi. Jab sab log pehle 1-2 saal apni magai aur project m the hum log khel rhe the XD. Roz aaspass ground pe training kr rhe h and then mess m ekdum late milke khana. Senator to tum banane hi the usko to koi nhi rok sakta tha lekin sacchi m itni khushi hui thi jb pata chala ki tum jeet gye (kyun naa hoti kuch log jinka naam nhi lunga tumhe underdog jo maan baithe the). Uttrakhand m bhi jamke maze kre the. Jab aadhe log apn mandir gye the, Kya scooty bhagayi thi yr :)) Aur tumhara wo turn pe slip to mention krna hi padega XD. Kaise bottle se petrol bhar bharke wapas hotel laute the XXD. 
Bas aise hi gyaan dete raho :p aur positivity maintain krte rho bhut jarurat h yr tumhare jaise logo ki <3. Delhi aaye to phir to kya hi kahna. nhi bhi aaye to bhi touch m rahna h. Keep laughing bro and iss saal ki trip ka compensation kro jaldi yr.
P.S. Jab shashi bolta h to sab sunte h
author: Kratik  Jain

text:
Yo madridista
The ultimate chaapu, dancer, dj and resaarcher XD. Shuru se hi apan saath rhe h. Pehle OnePlus gang, phir clasico rivals, antaragni partners (teri wajah se hi mein dance ke event dekha nhi to saara fun miss ho jaat bro), EDM guiders ğŸ˜‚ (humko hi kyun chalu krna hota tha yr) and shubham roasters. Tune kaafi gyaan diya h (in a positive way ofc) mujhe chahe music ho, dance ho, koi badiya app yaa food recommendation (which was rare for us veg people :'))
I respect you a lot for the things you have managed to achieve while still having fun, gossip and vibing. Hamesha genuine advice dene ke liye shukriya and i hope you manage to achieve what you aim for. So keep dancing, make others laugh and remain the genius you are.
Keep in touch bro. Take care. All the best. Puta madrid
